{"tid":1581104,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"六七3.0賀十一 - 陳也","createTime":"2019-09-19T11:39:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T11:40:03.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ae42eda7ef7e3b6847af930d76a80d6eb3adc550","tid":1581104,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T11:39:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F/daily/article/20190919/20770639\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E4%25B9%259F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190919%2F20770639&d=kSOQn%2BAsZtDywzIR1u7IP%2FsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=d76b6c10\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E4%25B9%259F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190919%2F20770639&h=d0c900f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F/daily/article/20190919/20770639</a><br />\n<br />\n六七3.0賀十一 - 陳也<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20190919/large/1568790870_a5b2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20190919%2Flarge%2F1568790870_a5b2.jpg&h=37f405ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「Freedom Hong Kong」fb圖片(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n姓林的黑警認為，開實彈的時機到了。以左輪回應李嘉誠先生的「不接受一切暴力包括語言暴力」。警暴無後顧之憂，語言和武力同時升級，雖然解放軍冇入城，64冇翻版，香港同樣將會血腥過凜冬烏克蘭。<br />\n<br />\n致命第一槍的目標名單排榜首的，無差別肯定是年輕人！殺一儆百，從各大學學生會落手，專揀李嘉誠先生口中的未來主人翁祭旗，網開一面？天方夜譚啊！黑警connect擲菠蘿的暴動始祖工聯會，後者以曱甴王稱呼李先生，繼做瓜國泰，打殘大班後，黑警出埋實彈，地產唔仆街？樓價唔跌返去中英聯合聲明的1984年？評級機構對六七3.0未敢恭維，負評「中港融合」只會鬥死香港。林奠趁國慶晚宴閉門呃商家佬，話中央會全力撐港。點撐？武警南下，喬裝北角福建佬，率領冇工開的旅巴司機全城暴走，有冇黑警實彈headshot都係一樣，全港恐襲！淪陷！政府強調過去三個月資金冇外流，中資等緊掃貨買起港企。中共70大壽前，特府奉旨黐&times;線，等賜死的林奠已經寫好遺囑咁，受益人除咗有英國居留權的家人，就是參加劈價16%的日韓團的腦殘藍絲！與話之佢十一死的有銀用撐警醫生！（簽未來醫生紙呃保險就好了，別揮動手術刀恫嚇同事好嗎？）勇和，未來十天要低調，避險。 <br />\n<br />\n陳也<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n校歌教我們的事 (曾志豪)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n提比利亞 (李純恩)"},{"pid":"71a77fa3a267657a5220e78c2d68f1ad3262e255","tid":1581104,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T11:39:52.000Z","msg":"【行動文宣】請廣傳<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">922 suck 4.0 各有各玩</span></span><br />\n1）影帝不死隊，入機場cover突擊隊<br />\n2）先塞青衣，再視乎情況轉戰商場<br />\n3）直接和理suck商場<br />\n4）全港交通測試，工程RB隊<br />\n5）加入單車隊-會有單車小將帶領<br />\n6）黨鐵突擊小隊！（機場突擊隊已有一定人數後）<br />\n7）東涌郊野一日遊，玩無線電walkie，玩無人機<br />\n8) 我係機場人-食錯藍絲野食物中毒 準備 SL 被罷工<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">兄弟爬山，各有各做</span><br />\n<del>我地另外有秘密小隊行動</del><br />\n<br />\nTG : <a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=kSOQn%2BAsZtDywzIR1u7IP%2FsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=12b53b60\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"02e105dd03d9d2978e586041fc8f7eae80f320ab","tid":1581104,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T11:40:03.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[公海 文宣 行動整合] 9.29全球抗赤納粹集會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1579667\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1579667</a><br />\n全世界一齊對準ChiNazi極權！</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BZiskWr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBZiskWr.png&h=b85bf973&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">9.29 Global AntiChiNazi 文宣、資訊、行動整合Channel</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/AntiChinazi929\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FAntiChinazi929&d=kSOQn%2BAsZtDywzIR1u7IP%2FsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=8818d0c0\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/AntiChinazi929</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>9.29 Global AntiChiNazi 公海</strong></span><br />\